  "culturalTip": "The Han River runs through the middle of Seoul and has twelve riverside parks along its banks. There are bicycle lanes, pedestrian walkways, and a few restaurants in the parks. Many people gather by the Han River when the weather is nice and have a picnic or ride a bike. Bike rentals are plentiful along the Han River, so don't worry if you don't own one!",
